      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I'm sorry to hear that you're not feeling well. It does sound like anxiety and possibly even a panic attack, but it's crucial to monitor your symptoms closely. While anxiety can cause these sensations, unusual chest pressure and lack of movement are concerning, so it may be wise to seek medical attention promptly, or at least consult with a healthcare professional if possible. Try some deep breathing exercises or calming techniques in the meantime, but prioritize getting checked out.",
