      "content": "It's understandable that you want to alleviate your discomfort. Diazepam, also known as Valium, can be effective for managing anxiety, but it's important to use it as prescribed by a healthcare professional. Taking more than usual can lead to dependency, withdrawal symptoms, or even overdose. I strongly recommend consulting your doctor or a healthcare provider before using more medication. They can provide the safest and most suitable treatment options. In the meantime, focusing on relaxation techniques and getting some rest might help stabilize your symptoms.",
